                          Extramural Grant Program

  Grant Application Reference Center:  A Compendium of Documents to Assist
                              Grant Applicants

     * FY 2001 Program Announcement for the Extramural Grant Program
     * Grant Application Form PHS 5161-1 (includes Standard Forms [SF]-424
       and SF-424A)
     * Contract Information for Negotiating Indirect Cost Rates
     * "Increasing Donation and Transplantation: The Challenge of
       Evaluation"
     * Final Report of the April 1998 conference, "Increasing Donation and
       Transplantation: The Challenge of Evaluation"
     * Analysis of State Actions Regarding Donor Registries
     * FY 1999 Grant Awards
     * FY 2000 Grant Awards
     * FY 2001 Grant Awards
     * IOM study report abstract: "Non-Heart-Beating Organ
       Transplantation: Medical and Ethical Issues in Procurement"
     * IOM study report abstract: "Non-Heart-Beating Organ
       Transplantation: Practice and Protocols"
     * 45 CFR Part 46
     * Belmont Report
     * State Single Point of Contact List (SPOC)
     * OMB Circulars: A-87, A-21, and A-122 (Cost Principles Circulars);
       and A-133 (Audit Requirements Circular)
     * PHS Grant Policy Statement
     * Form HHS 690
     __________________________________________________________________

